125
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,640
L'Amérique.

126
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:54,640
C'est là que j'ai entrevu l'avenir.

127
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:57,600
Les casinos.

128
00:09:58,160 --> 00:09:59,520
Des usines à fric.

129
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,320
Écoute,

130
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:03,560
