133
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,480
- Montre.
- Tout est là.

134
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:13,560
Il y a moyen de faire fortune.

135
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:15,840
Je suis vieux

136
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:18,360
